summary:
As business owner I am responsible for the product and innovation lifecycle of network, campus, education services and product development.

I help people to take the next step in creating and realizing their ideas and dreams so that they can grow and flourish. 

I get my inspiration and creativity from the close collaboration with progressive colleagues with whom we meet every challenge with open arms.

I want to continuously develop my (personal) leadership style so that it enables me to let our organization, the team and myself rise above ourselves.
